	ASCII Tetris game
=================================

 To compile, use:

 make

 It will output a binary file Tetris.

 Controls:

  q: 		left
  s: 		bottom (quicker)
  d: 		right
  [space]: 	rotate

   [LEVEL: 1 | SCORE: 0]
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  !                        !
  !                        !
  !                        !
  !                        !
  !          O O           !
  !          O             !
  !          O             !
  !                        !
  !                        !
  !                        !
  !                        !
  !              &         !
  !              &         !
  !      # #   X & &       !
  !      # # X X X @ @ @ @ !
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

